sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Controller
    participant APIServer as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Kueue Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Kueue Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Cache as Kueue Cache<br/>In-Process
    participant Scheduler as Kueue Scheduler<br/>In-Process
    participant Queue as Queue Manager<br/>In-Process
    participant AdmCheck as Admission Check Controller<br/>In-Process
    participant Autoscaler as Cluster Autoscaler<br/>Varies HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission
    User->>APIServer: POST Job (Batch/PyTorch/TF/MPI/Ray/JobSet)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token or Kubeconfig
    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /mutate-*<br/>mTLS (API Server)
    Webhook-->>APIServer: Mutated Job (queue.name label)
    APIServer-->>User: Job Created

    Controller->>APIServer: Watch Job/Workload CRDs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    APIServer-->>Controller: Job Event
    Controller->>Controller: Create Workload CR
    Controller->>Cache: Update Queue State<br/>In-Process
    Cache-->>Controller: State Updated

    Controller->>Scheduler: Check Admission<br/>In-Process
    Scheduler->>Cache: Get ClusterQueue State<br/>In-Process
    Cache-->>Scheduler: Available Quota
    Scheduler-->>Controller: Admission Decision

    alt Quota Available
        Controller->>APIServer: Admit Workload (Update Status)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        APIServer-->>Controller: Workload Admitted
        Controller->>APIServer: Unsuspend Job (Remove suspend=true)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        APIServer-->>User: Job Running (Pods Created)
    else No Quota - Provisioning Check Required
        Controller->>AdmCheck: Trigger ProvisioningACC<br/>In-Process
        AdmCheck->>APIServer: Create ProvisioningRequest<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        APIServer->>Autoscaler: Provision Nodes<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Autoscaler-->>APIServer: Nodes Provisioning
        APIServer-->>AdmCheck: ProvisioningRequest Accepted
        AdmCheck-->>Controller: Admission Check Passed
        Controller->>APIServer: Admit Workload<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    else No Quota - Queued
        Controller->>Queue: Enqueue Workload<br/>In-Process (StrictFIFO/BestEffortFIFO)
        Queue-->>Controller: Workload Queued
    end

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 2: Workload Status Query (Visibility API)
    User->>APIServer: GET /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/pendingworkloads<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    APIServer->>APIServer: RBAC Check
    APIServer->>Webhook: Proxy Request to Visibility Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTPS TLS
    Webhook->>Queue: Query Pending Workloads<br/>In-Process
    Queue-->>Webhook: Pending Workloads List
    Webhook-->>APIServer: JSON Response
    APIServer-->>User: Pending Workloads Data

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Autoscaler->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Controller-->>Autoscaler: Prometheus Metrics<br/>(queue depth, admission rates, resource usage)
